106100
106200     IF      CH-NF-NOV               =       "S"     OR
106300             IA1                     >      ZEROS
106400             GO                      TO      070-S-PLACSOR
106500     ELSE
106600             NEXT    SENTENCE.
106700
106800     MOVE    "S"                     TO      CH-CHASSI.
106900     MOVE    NPL-LETRA               TO      TBB-LETRA (IX1).
107000     MOVE    NPL-NUMERO              TO      TBB-NUMER (IX1).
