171300             MOVE ZEROS              TO     OUT-RESTFIN
171400                                            OUT-CNPJ-FIN
171500                                            OUT-CNPJ-AGFIN
171600             MOVE SPACES             TO     OUT-NOME-FIN
171700                                            OUT-NOME-AGFIN
171800             GO                      170-S-GRAVAMESDS
171900         ELSE
