172100             CALL    SYSTEM  DMTERMINATE.
172200
172300
172400     MOVE    GRA-TIPO-RESTR          TO     OUT-RESTFIN.
172500     MOVE    GRA-CPF-CGC-FINAN       TO     OUT-CNPJ-FIN.
172600     MOVE    GRA-NOME-FINANC         TO     OUT-NOME-FIN.
172700     MOVE    GRA-CGC-AGENTE          TO     OUT-CNPJ-AGFIN.
172800     MOVE    GRA-NOME-AGENTE         TO     OUT-NOME-AGFIN.
