175500     MOVE    AX-LENGTH               TO      COMS-OUT-TEXT-LENGTH.
175600     MOVE    0                       TO      COMS-OUT-STATUS.
175700     MOVE    COMS-IN-STATION         TO      COMS-OUT-DESTINATION.
